    {
      "name": "实时计算",
      "description": "基于评估数据的实时成本计算",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "计算项目成本",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"risk_scores\": {\n    \"架构\": 15,\n    \"流程\": 10\n  },\n  \"roles\": [\n    {\n      \"role_name\": \"前端工程师\",\n      \"unit_price\": 1800\n    },\n    {\n      \"role_name\": \"后端工程师\",\n      \"unit_price\": 2000\n    }\n  ],\n  \"development_workload\": [\n    {\n      \"delivery_factor\": 1,\n      \"前端工程师\": 20,\n      \"后端工程师\": 30\n    }\n  ],\n  \"integration_workload\": [\n    {\n      \"delivery_factor\": 1.1,\n      \"前端工程师\": 8,\n      \"后端工程师\": 12\n    }\n  ],\n  \"travel_months\": 2,\n  \"travel_headcount\": 3,\n  \"maintenance_months\": 1,\n  \"maintenance_headcount\": 2,\n  \"maintenance_daily_cost\": 1600,\n  \"risk_items\": [\n    {\n      \"cost\": 2.5\n    }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}{{api_prefix}}/calculate",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "calculate"]
            },
            "description": "根据评估数据实时计算成本与工作量\n\n**请求字段:**\n- `risk_scores`: 风险评分对象\n- `roles`: 角色配置数组\n- `development_workload`: 开发工作量数组\n- `integration_workload`: 集成工作量数组\n- `travel_months`: 差旅月数\n- `travel_headcount`: 差旅人数\n- `maintenance_months`: 维护月数\n- `maintenance_headcount`: 维护人数\n- `maintenance_daily_cost`: 维护日成本\n- `risk_items`: 风险成本项数组\n\n**注意:** 角色单价单位为\"元\"，返回金额单位为\"万元\""
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
